## § 2.0 Project Overview

I am a language learner who is trying to practice the vocabulary she is learning. As of now, there is not a flashcard tool accessible online that meets her needs. Often, flashcard apps have too many features or require a membership. She wants an app/website that she can use both on her laptop and mobile devices (phone and tablet) that she can use to create and practice the vocabulary. She wants a simple website that focuses on creating and practicing the vocabulary. As for an organizational system, she would like the flashcards to be organizable such as by topic (color, food, places, etc.) via a tagging system. Also it would be nice to have a feature that allows the flashcards to be organized into folders which could be named after the date they were created or a lesson where she found the words. The goal is to keep the app/website simple. All coding, when able to, should be done using Svelte.

